Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.58,0:00:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.78,0:00:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.25,0:00:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.79,0:00:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.90,0:00:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.11,0:00:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.91,0:00:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.19,0:01:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.63,0:01:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.30,0:01:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.94,0:01:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.64,0:01:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.40,0:01:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac175年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.90,0:01:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的领导者被暗杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.44,0:01:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5部钢弹被派往地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.77,0:01:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本应为了报复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.48,0:01:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但OZ在宇宙的行动并非支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.51,0:01:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于他们全面提出和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.12,0:01:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星认同OZ了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.26,0:01:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.62,0:01:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在支配地球和宇宙的进程中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.19,0:01:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹被视作叛军\N的象征给孤立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.73,0:02:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无家可归的钢弹和其驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.30,0:02:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在不断转变的时代里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.07,0:02:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以存在意义为赌注的继续战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.31,0:02:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没打中?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避过了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.42,0:02:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚，有另一个了解我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.79,0:02:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是关怀我\N拥有两颗心灵的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行动是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.89,0:02:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我这行动也是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.03,0:02:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十三话\N[变回死神的迪欧]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.75,0:02:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,压舱物的调整要慢慢来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.62,0:02:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，用灯照那里的岩石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.52,0:02:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行过多次战斗却没有损毁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.43,0:03:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有船接近这海域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.07,0:03:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛把这部钢弹弃在海里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.10,0:03:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,声东击西，而自己就飞上宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.01,0:03:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是机动战士潜水空母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ当然会来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.98,0:03:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是危险的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你不要担心相信雇佣兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是前联合深海部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大显身手的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.88,0:03:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派西斯准备出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.05,0:03:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一时方向确认反射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.72,0:03:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是01
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.59,0:03:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!坎沙出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体开始攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确认螺旋声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敌人机动战士!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.18,0:03:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坎沙部队!快回答!坎沙部队!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然抛下钢弹离去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有什么打算呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，这部机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会创造今后的时代啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是量产型也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用计较成本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙有无限的资源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想把宇宙卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.55,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变回本来的宇宙殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.55,0:05:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晚会让他知道厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.49,0:05:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.59,0:05:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你运那东西去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是你们偷了我们的技术后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解体了的钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真荣幸呢，想不到变成废铁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.03,0:05:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也会引起你的兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.24,0:05:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?\N我对那种东西没兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.94,0:05:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点丢掉它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，技师长大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.31,0:05:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,制造比钢弹更优良的机动战士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了，别那样催我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.06,0:05:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们有太多事要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你们久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.73,0:05:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然只剩下装修啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙不是有讨厌战争的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,独立思想吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在为何一定要拿起武器?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星只是实验设施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.99,0:06:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经是百年以前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了避免战斗，我们决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武装起来也是迫不得已的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.56,0:06:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉‧普奥，前联合军少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在是反OZ叛乱份子的一员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支持及指挥各地的秘密活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.70,0:06:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有情报说他们得到01和04
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推动OZ的罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.07,0:06:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是地球上最强大的组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.54,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那组织里也有若干问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.95,0:06:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们想保护卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我们认同了OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.65,0:06:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寻求更高更可靠的安全性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球继续着武力斗争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是从它的影响中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.96,0:06:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保护自己而选择的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.19,0:06:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球对抗OZ的人认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.80,0:07:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉住那班钢弹技师的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.33,0:07:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才是想把这世界\N变为极危险的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.64,0:07:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们收到报告说\N技师已经被处死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.21,0:07:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦是避免再次出现那种叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.14,0:07:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有力量就不能\N维持国家的尊严
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.81,0:07:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的决定不会改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.12,0:07:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特大使，请你明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.09,0:07:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀了技师?不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种假情报才不得不最害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,物资和零件已经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从各个工场卫星运来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.41,0:07:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到OZ协助的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经准备在月面工场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.48,0:07:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,量产最新型的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.58,0:07:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不用再害怕侵略的恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为特列斯统帅和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校的努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.19,0:07:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙才能迎接新时代的到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亏你们说得出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那两人会为你们带来战争的恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.20,0:08:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以往卫星一直在屈辱的历史里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.97,0:08:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不害怕令卫星站起来的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是希尔妲‧舒拜嘉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个卫星的志愿兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的士兵吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁也会批评
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个卫星的大部份学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,报名担任月面工场的守卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.69,0:08:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要知道行动才是信念的表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.22,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.73,0:08:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我也报名试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次兵役检查在一星期后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有意思就参加试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请务必让我参加啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我押去月面基地吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.95,0:09:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我做新型机的测试驾驶员吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作新型机的目标吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.09,0:09:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ也认同你的胆色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.06,0:09:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ和其母体罗姆斐拉的战略目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.23,0:09:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是令地球圈统一联合崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.84,0:09:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到地球的支配权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.47,0:09:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何不干脆支配卫星?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.98,0:09:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配毫无防备的卫星对OZ来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.65,0:09:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就等于扭断婴儿的手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.72,0:09:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他或许能理解啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.79,0:09:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯希望决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自以为是的卫星会知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.42,0:09:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们和特列斯力量上的差距吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.03,0:09:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体快点准备上船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢，辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?找我有事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我应该说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.72,0:10:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招募新志愿兵在一星期后啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我看一下那张报名表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这张很完美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但这是伪造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里欧被抢走了!追!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.98,0:10:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要动!\N我不想在卫星内开炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.48,0:10:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃得掉吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是破坏月面工场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但路程这样就太远了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.93,0:10:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不会手下留情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫无实战经验的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警告也不会有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.04,0:11:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了卫星的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也为了卫星在战斗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.35,0:11:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标进入射程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.49,0:11:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.96,0:11:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!我们为了卫星在战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.43,0:11:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们为何变成敌人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.54,0:11:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说过我们不是敌人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.68,0:11:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是志愿兵，发誓效忠OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有心理准备随时牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.58,0:11:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的大无畏精神令我吃惊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!走开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.22,0:12:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧‧麦斯威尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你是钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何要救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.50,0:12:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有心理准备随时牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想被敌人同情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫希尔妲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说的敌人谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.77,0:12:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星何时起变成\N战争中的组织?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前联合从地球攻来时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.51,0:12:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑容从卫星的所有人面上消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了得回那笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直在战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑容回到卫星又如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.39,0:12:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家不是亲自在抛掉笑容吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.43,0:12:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.89,0:12:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星何时起变得不正常?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的战争状态影响到宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.53,0:12:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙已经不能再束手待毙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是宇宙的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.47,0:13:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真勇敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.71,0:13:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们载我去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.65,0:13:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那里审问你有关钢弹的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.62,0:13:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的目的是破坏月面基地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不会做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.25,0:13:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何不当我是敌人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会让你得逞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恕我直言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.69,0:13:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以你的力量根本不是我的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种家伙竟然\N豁出性命和我对抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我觉得你不顾后果的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.60,0:13:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和独自挑战地球的我很相似
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.81,0:13:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一定是傻瓜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.81,0:13:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,士兵何时死去也不出奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.18,0:13:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的同伴今后会有多人牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.25,0:13:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们尽力走自己相信的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是那么傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不能成为士兵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问到什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.43,0:14:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.63,0:14:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,班长，刚才的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威吓射击不是也可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.67,0:14:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命令说杀死叛乱份子也不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.61,0:14:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.01,0:14:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使自己人被牵连也一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.21,0:14:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希尔妲特士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.35,0:14:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但士兵要有心理准备随时牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了任务啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,征兵班长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.22,0:14:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即将到达月面基地上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我们的穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.96,0:14:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前往OZ的军事设施移交俘虏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三引擎发生火警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.24,0:14:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像被人从内部炸毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.69,0:14:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了吗? 果然聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在要炸开舱门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想受伤就退后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!迪欧!迪欧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才的爆炸是什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?报告情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.23,0:15:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平衡器无效，很不利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.70,0:16:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到达月球了，很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死期到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以我来说算做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.83,0:16:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来!快点了结我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.93,0:16:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但输给机器令我有点生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.08,0:17:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!发出自己人的识别讯号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.09,0:17:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会没命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能发出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.36,0:17:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我已经不知道谁是自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧，快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去做你想做的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希尔妲，你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.21,0:17:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也只是照自己意思尽力去做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.89,0:17:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，我现在救不了你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.03,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说过吧，我有心理准备牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...希尔妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.81,0:18:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要白白送死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是呢，迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希尔妲!你做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先放下枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行动非常有问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来在地底吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经通风系统就会直达工场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那里!捉住他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人入侵B6区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在追击中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.39,0:18:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.32,0:18:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人企图破坏机动战士工场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?派守卫去地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻止他入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.74,0:19:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.64,0:19:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.75,0:19:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.62,0:19:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四个也来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是杀死我们吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.02,0:19:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久没见了，迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.99,0:19:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.19,0:19:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，是新机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧，你想驾驶它吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.83,0:19:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何时完成?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.00,0:19:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个月后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前\N你无论如何也要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.57,0:19:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，机会也会降临你身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.44,0:19:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!这边!快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.25,0:19:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧，快下决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.81,0:19:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以给人发现这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.22,0:19:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.05,0:19:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了，没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，快点开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能拜托你吗?老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.29,0:20:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌的任务啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.47,0:20:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫出来会没那么痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.28,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但…我是男子汉呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.82,0:20:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙忘掉养育之恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然想杀死我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.53,0:20:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不会让人\N阻碍我们的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务失败吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.87,0:20:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你破坏不了基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又杀不了博士他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.91,0:20:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别那样说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…值得我来这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.78,0:20:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.58,0:21:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我的正在改良啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.46,0:21:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ看来会暂时让我们活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得的机会\N你不要这么快死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.60,0:21:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.90,0:21:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会那么轻易就死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.90,0:21:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了卫星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等着瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.81,0:21:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定会再次变成死神啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.31,0:21:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.88,0:21:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陪同匹斯克拉福特大使回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.38,0:21:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,护卫任务完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.42,0:21:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.69,0:21:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大使也明白\N宇宙决心的坚定了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.06,0:21:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为杰克斯‧马吉斯又如何呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也是对时代有意见的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晚也会再有战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.73,0:21:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到时再下结论吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.93,0:21:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无人能阻止历史的洪流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.20,0:21:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是特列斯大人也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我把历史移去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.58,0:22:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人的理想那里就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.88,0:22:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为此，我也能豁出性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.28,0:22:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要战斗，赢取未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赢取特列斯大人的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.02,0:22:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有我的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.49,0:22:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.94,0:22:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.94,0:22:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.94,0:22:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.94,0:22:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.44,0:22:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.94,0:23:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.44,0:23:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.94,0:23:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.94,0:23:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.00,0:23:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切变得疯狂的宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.04,0:23:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有毁灭一途吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.61,0:23:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常酷似钢弹的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.51,0:23:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陆续攻击武装起来的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.78,0:23:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦和希洛前去迎击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.85,0:23:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,强力的新型机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.95,0:23:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但驾驶它的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.75,0:23:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充满冰冷愤怒和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.19,0:23:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无限悲伤的卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.86,0:23:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新机动战记-钢弹W，第二十四话
